name: Official Wild 'N Out
description: Official Wild ‘N Out is a cryptocurrency project inspired by the hit improv comedy and rap battle show Wild ‘N Out, created and hosted by Nick Cannon. The project combines meme culture with real utility, aiming to build a strong, engaged community while offering exclusive rewards and experiences for holders. Official Wild ‘N Out is brought to you by Nick Cannon, the creator and host of Wild ‘N Out. As a multi-talented entertainer and entrepreneur, Cannon is expanding the brand into Web3, offering fans and crypto enthusiasts a way to engage with the Wild ‘N Out community in new ways.
